id: pm-quzx
title: Canonicalize dual beads/todos package implementations and define external-package dependency-range policy
description: "Choose one canonical implementation each for Beads and Todos integrations, redirect or retire duplicates, and enforce one verified pm-cli dependency-range policy across all external ecosystem packages."
type: Chore
status: open
priority: 2
tags[3]: ecosystem,governance,packages
created_at: "2026-07-15T19:40:58.243Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-17T21:45:41.266Z"
author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 240
acceptance_criteria: "Canonical home decided per package (extend an existing implementation, never a third); non-canonical repo README points to the canonical package and repo is archived or repurposed; capability divergence documented (external pm-beads import+export+validate+diff+bead_id schema vs in-repo import-only) with migration note; ecosystem dependency-range convention documented (caret year-range with verified floor; no exact pins, no unbounded >=) and pm-ops exact-pin 2026.7.13 plus pm-beads >=2026.7.10 ranges fixed; floor-verification folded into the reusable ecosystem smoke harness or the pm-o8um Verified-tier checklist"
parent: pm-ugqx
risk: medium
confidence: high
